    <h2 class="section-title">Eight reasons.</h2>

    <ul class="why-list">
      <li><strong>Cleaning service that actually solves the problem.</strong> 60% of "no ice" emergency calls resolve through proper cleaning. Many shops don't bother with cleaning service and lose customers to recurring repair tickets.</li>
